pageTitle: Midwest Dairy Association Announces Internship in Illinois | Hoards Dairyman
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {6555=02.06.2013, 7932=Midwest Dairy Association’s Industry Relations team has announced the availability of a paid internship in Springfield, Illinois for the summer of 2013. Applications are due March 4, 2013. The internship provides an opportunity for students interested in communications, public relations, marketing, food science or agribusiness., 7445=The intern will gain practical experience in communication, public relations and marketing programs for dairy products. Job duties include writing news releases and website materials, assisting with promotional activities during June Dairy Month and at the Illinois State Fair, and coordinating displays and materials.}
